12:35.949 --> 12:37.448
You're never late?

12:38.485 --> 12:41.288
Hey, Kirk, Juan here
says you're lying.

12:41.423 --> 12:43.960
Juan's a free man.
He can say whatever he wants.

12:46.327 --> 12:47.492
You know, Juan,
you show up late again,

12:47.627 --> 12:49.398
I'm gonna have to fire you.
That's the rules.

12:49.533 --> 12:51.462
Yes, sir.

12:53.270 --> 12:55.663
DYLAN: Hey, you know
what somebody else told me?

12:55.799 --> 12:57.204
That he found your lariat
just laying

12:57.339 --> 12:58.704
in the front of the stable
on the ground.

12:58.840 --> 13:00.506
Is that true?

13:00.642 --> 13:02.176
No, sir.

13:12.616 --> 13:16.419
T.T., your Purge
protection bonus.

13:16.555 --> 13:18.856
-Thank you, Mr. Tucker.
-Stay safe.

13:18.991 --> 13:19.988
Thank you, sir.

13:20.123 --> 13:21.525
Kirk.

13:33.504 --> 13:36.540
You're doing a good job, Juan.

13:36.675 --> 13:40.241
My son's a hair rattled
'cause of yesterday.

13:40.377 --> 13:41.912
Don't take offense.

13:42.047 --> 13:43.916
Thank you, sir.

13:44.052 --> 13:46.055
I really appreciate that.

13:49.321 --> 13:51.357
Can I be honest, Mr. Tucker?

13:53.190 --> 13:54.657
