or from somewhere else.

14:12.579 --> 14:14.281
I know that a lot of people
feel that way,

14:14.417 --> 14:16.285
but I'm not sure
that's the case with Dylan.

14:16.421 --> 14:19.218
Uh, he's a very proud man.
You one-upped him yesterday.

14:19.354 --> 14:21.354
You're a damn fine cowboy,
Juan.

14:23.122 --> 14:24.555
I don't know, sir.

14:29.126 --> 14:30.995
Well...

14:31.131 --> 14:32.897
I don't know either.

14:33.032 --> 14:34.565
I just...

14:36.075 --> 14:38.504
I always taught my son
to be a proud American,

14:38.639 --> 14:41.212
