has been fully cleansed.

28:28.701 --> 28:33.234
We will no longer tolerate
foreigners raping and pillaging

28:33.370 --> 28:36.103
the United States of America.

28:36.239 --> 28:38.307
Do not try to hide.

28:38.442 --> 28:42.776
We will find you
and disinfect you.

28:42.911 --> 28:47.153
America will be
American once again.

28:50.055 --> 28:51.454
LEAD MERC:
Hey.

28:52.954 --> 28:55.557
Where'd you learn
to handle a weapon like that?

29:47.380 --> 29:50.313
-

29:50.448 --> 29:52.655
-MAN: Oh, my God.
-

29:52.790 --> 29:55.683
-It's over.
-

30:04.362 --> 30:07.061
WOMAN:
We made it through.

30:08.735 --> 30:11.369
-WOMAN: I see you. I see you.

30:21.986 --> 30:24.087
Harp?
Come on, let's get to work.

30:27.517 --> 30:29.926
-Harper.
-Sis, come on, let's go.

30:36.529 --> 30:38.200
The day after the Purge
should be a holiday.

30:38.336 --> 30:39.469
No?

30:39.605 --> 30:41.436
¿Qué es un holiday?

30:41.571 --> 30:43.533
Holiday? Mm.

30:47.503 --> 30:49.044
Another day, another dollar.

30:50.943 --> 30:52.607
Mira.

30:52.742 --> 30:56.484
teardrop falls

30:58.724 --> 31:00.385
T.T.:
Ah, chingado.

31:04.426 --> 31:07.930
-

31:08.065 --> 31:12.133
teardrop falls

31:28.648 --> 31:30.854
NEWSMAN
...busy, jubilant street,

31:30.990 --> 31:33.121
sanitation crews
are out in full force

31:33.256 --> 31:35.817
with the macabre task
of disinfecting streets

31:35.952 --> 31:38.292
and cleaning corpses
from sidewalks and roadways.

31:38.427 --> 31:41.593
The Purge is over,
and now the cleanup has begun.

31:41.729 --> 31:44.593
All over the state, violent
incidents ended hours ago...

31:44.728 --> 31:46.700
-MAN Fake news!
-

32:17.803 --> 32:19.860
ADELA:
Where is everybody?

33:06.577 --> 33:08.381
What the hell?

34:09.947 --> 34:11.480
ADELA:
!Ayúdenme!

34:11.615 --> 34:12.843
Help!

34:16.279 --> 34:17.483
Help!

34:20.989 --> 34:22.624
Help!

34:44.343 --> 34:45.846
You can't do this today!

34:45.981 --> 34:47.150
The Purge is over!

34:47.285 --> 34:48.949
-MAN: No, no.
-

34:49.085 --> 34:50.543
This is the Forever Purge.

34:50.679 --> 34:51.554
It's never stopping.

34:51.690 --> 34:53.319
!Ayúdenme!

34:53.454 --> 34:54.490
Thank you
for your participation.

34:54.625 --> 34:55.552
Fuck!

34:55.688 --> 34:57.720
-

34:57.855 --> 34:59.058
-

34:59.194 --> 35:01.362
!Ayúdenme! Help!

35:02.629 --> 35:05.197
But the Purge is over!

35:05.332 --> 35:07.329
-Help!

35:11.040 --> 35:13.070
ADELA:
Boss!

35:16.607 --> 35:17.642
ADELA:
Watch out!

35:20.683 --> 35:22.350
MAN: You're gonna fucking die!
You're all gonna die!

35:23.550 --> 35:25.049
-ADELA: Help! Boss!

35:27.716 --> 35:29.016
ADELA:
Be careful!

35:30.085 --> 35:31.186
-

35:31.321 --> 35:32.393
Boss!

35:33.963 --> 35:34.927
Are you okay?

35:39.201 --> 35:41.200
-You okay?
-Yes.

35:41.336 --> 35:42.737
-Come here.

35:43.909 --> 35:45.206
-You all right?
-Yes.

35:45.341 --> 35:47.742
-

35:49.506 --> 35:51.372
Fuck you!

35:51.507 --> 35:53.348
Fuck you!

36:00.384 --> 36:02.918
Go! Darius, go!

36:03.721 --> 36:05.089
-

36:07.023 --> 36:09.094
-

36:09.229 --> 36:10.796
Drop your weapon!

36:10.931 --> 36:13.533
-On your knees. Drop it.
-DARIUS: We didn't do anything.

36:13.668 --> 36:14.731
-Get on your knees.
-Get on your knees.

36:14.867 --> 36:16.900
-They attacked us!
-We didn't do anything.

36:17.035 --> 36:18.765
The Purge is over, lady.
What the hell are you doing?

36:18.901 --> 36:21.443
ADELA:
Sir, this is a mistake!

36:21.578 --> 36:23.107
-Wait, please! -DARIUS:
We didn't do anything wrong!

36:23.243 --> 36:24.109
Listen to me.

36:24.244 --> 36:26.579
Listen to us, sir!

36:30.285 --> 36:32.755
JUAN:
It's so quiet.

36:32.890 --> 36:34.719
Where is everyone?

36:40.361 --> 36:41.389
JUAN:
Oh, come on.

36:41.525 --> 36:43.260
Stop the car.

36:55.407 --> 36:57.247
Well, well, well.

37:02.579 --> 37:04.313
Look at this.

37:14.562 --> 37:16.662
This feels like
fucking Christmas.

37:17.729 --> 37:19.764
Any of y'all get me a present?

37:21.264 --> 37:24.631
Caleb, I know you did,
and let me tell you, sir...

37:24.767 --> 37:27.475
I spent your money well.

37:30.074 --> 37:31.807
Today's your day
of reckoning, cowboy.

37:31.942 --> 37:33.210
-

37:33.346 --> 37:36.680
You become me

37:36.816 --> 37:40.050
-and I become you, huh?
-

37:40.186 --> 37:43.184
The old switcheroo is happening
on every ranch around here.

37:43.319 --> 37:46.725
You and all your rich-ass
neighbors will find out

37:46.860 --> 37:49.457
what it's like to be
penniless and powerless.

37:49.593 --> 37:50.795
To be like us!

37:52.270 --> 37:53.894
These rich motherfuckers
can't hide

37:54.029 --> 37:55.567
behind their steel walls
no more.

37:55.703 --> 37:58.732
This is the way
things are now, boys!

37:58.867 --> 38:00.507
This Purge is forever!

38:00.643 --> 38:01.701
-MAN: Yeah.

38:01.837 --> 38:03.538
This is the real Purge.

38:03.673 --> 38:05.176
The eternal Purge.

38:05.311 --> 38:07.477
Ever After!

38:07.613 --> 38:09.248
MEN:
Ever After!

38:14.049 --> 38:16.183
T.T.:
Ay, cabrón.

38:16.318 --> 38:18.854
-I'm gonna give you a chance

38:18.990 --> 38:20.691
to save your family,
Dylan Tucker,

38:20.827 --> 38:24.100
one by one,
but you'll have to pay.

38:24.236 --> 38:26.230
-Let's start with

38:26.365 --> 38:29.236
eeny, meeny,

38:29.372 --> 38:30.767
-miny, ho!
-

38:30.903 --> 38:32.267
How much would you give
for her, Dylan?

38:32.403 --> 38:34.670
How much would you give to
stop me from putting a bullet

38:34.805 --> 38:36.905
in your baby sister's head?

38:37.041 --> 38:39.745
Let's say ten bucks,
and she lives.

38:39.880 --> 38:41.712
Oh, that seems like
a fair market price

38:41.848 --> 38:43.351
for this broke-down,
useless woman.

38:43.486 --> 38:45.548
Let's see
how much money you got.

38:45.684 --> 38:47.422
Aw, shit, Dylan! I forgot.

38:47.557 --> 38:50.360
You're me now,
which means you're broke.

38:51.727 --> 38:53.759
You have no money.
That sucks, doesn't it?

38:54.825 --> 38:58.263
See, Dylan, without money,

38:58.398 --> 39:00.261
you have no power.

39:00.397 --> 39:03.804
Without money, you can't save
your own little sister,

39:03.940 --> 39:06.370
-and she will die because
of it. -

39:06.506 --> 39:09.269
But how's that feel?

39:10.345 --> 39:11.876
How's that feel, Dylan?

39:14.575 --> 39:17.046
-Feels like shit, doesn't it?
-

39:18.054 --> 39:19.415
That's my life.

39:19.551 --> 39:20.483
It's our life.

39:20.619 --> 39:22.419
That's how we feel.

39:22.555 --> 39:24.954
That's how we have felt

39:25.090 --> 39:26.925
every day
since the day we were born!

39:27.060 --> 39:29.389
And I want you to fucking feel
that fucking pain

39:29.524 --> 39:31.126
-in your fucking stomach,
Dylan! -

39:31.261 --> 39:32.332
Goddamn it,
it looks like the old man's

39:32.467 --> 39:33.733
got something to say! What?!

39:33.868 --> 39:35.628
Damn it! You're right, Kirk!
You're right!

39:35.763 --> 39:37.405
-You're right! -I don't give
a fuck if you think I'm right!

39:37.541 --> 39:39.905
You're talking about
life in America,

39:40.040 --> 39:42.842
the way the rich get rich
off the backs of the poor,

39:42.977 --> 39:46.642
the way it's been
ever since we robbed this land

39:46.778 --> 39:49.116
from the Native Americans.

39:49.252 --> 39:51.786
But you got no right

39:51.921 --> 39:56.421
to complain about the
very system you're supporting

39:56.556 --> 39:57.656
by picking up that gun

39:57.792 --> 39:59.159
and sanctioning
the goddamn Purge...

39:59.294 --> 40:01.022
We need more guns.

40:01.158 --> 40:02.663
CALEB:
...which is all about money.

40:05.933 --> 40:09.000
You know who created
the Purge, don't ya?

40:09.135 --> 40:14.376
A bunch of fat, rich
businessmen in Washington, D.C.

40:14.512 --> 40:17.111
So what would
that make you, Kirk?

40:17.247 --> 40:19.381
What would it make you?

40:19.517 --> 40:23.348
Huh? That would make you
their lackey

40:23.484 --> 40:26.116
and a goddamn hypocrite.

40:26.251 --> 40:29.620
They expect you to go out there
and do their violence,

40:29.755 --> 40:31.327
so they can play more golf.

40:31.463 --> 40:32.660
They've never even been
in a fistfight.

40:36.626 --> 40:38.727
So...

40:38.862 --> 40:41.630
from my family to you,

40:41.765 --> 40:43.833
go fuck yourself.

40:43.969 --> 40:45.200
-

40:46.970 --> 40:48.677
JUAN:
Puto.

40:49.680 --> 40:51.371
-

40:54.979 --> 40:56.684
-Take cover!
-

40:59.023 --> 41:00.183
We need backup!

41:00.318 --> 41:02.624
MAN
Copy that. We're on our way.

41:12.398 --> 41:14.101
Harper.

41:15.801 --> 41:16.666
T.T.:
What the fuck?!

41:16.801 --> 41:17.836
What the fuck, Kirk?!

41:17.972 --> 41:19.832
-Dad?
-The Purge is over, cabrón!

41:19.967 --> 41:21.544
Ever After.

41:28.587 --> 41:30.516
-The Purge is over, man!
-

41:33.688 --> 41:35.618
Cuidado. They're coming.

41:39.991 --> 41:41.394
JUAN:
You need to get up here.

41:41.530 --> 41:42.695
-Go!
-T.T.: Let's go!

41:42.831 --> 41:44.199
JUAN:
You need to get your family!

41:44.335 --> 41:45.727
T.T.:
Harper! Come on!

41:45.862 --> 41:47.432
Harper! Let's go.

41:47.568 --> 41:49.436
Let's go, let's go.

41:49.571 --> 41:51.233
-Come on!
-Come on.

41:54.002 --> 41:55.569
T.T.:
Come on.

41:55.705 --> 41:57.338
Come in.

42:05.249 --> 42:06.619
DISPATCHER
10-13, we have

42:06.754 --> 42:08.985
three more incidences reported.

42:09.121 --> 42:10.718
-Return to precinct.
-

42:10.853 --> 42:11.928
Copy that.

42:12.063 --> 42:13.152
This is insane.

42:13.287 --> 42:15.290
People not hear the sirens?

42:15.426 --> 42:17.125
-A little busier than
last year, huh? -Yeah.

42:17.260 --> 42:19.332
MAN:
I shouldn't even be here.

42:19.468 --> 42:21.197
I did nothing wrong.

42:22.707 --> 42:24.671
There's no such thing
as crime anymore.

42:27.409 --> 42:29.135
Let me fucking go!

42:29.270 --> 42:30.945
Would you shut the fuck up?

42:31.081 --> 42:31.981
Make me.

42:34.483 --> 42:35.985
What's going on, Darius?

42:36.121 --> 42:38.017
I don't know.

42:38.152 --> 42:40.150
-

42:42.059 --> 42:43.252
Adela.

42:48.491 --> 42:50.022
DYLAN: All right,
let me check the radio.

42:50.158 --> 42:51.257
Maybe there's some news.

42:51.392 --> 42:53.168
NEWSMAN:
People are still purging

42:53.304 --> 42:54.628
all across the country.

42:54.764 --> 42:56.871
"Ever After Purge" is popping
up all over social media,

42:57.006 --> 42:58.869
continuous purging dubbed
the "Forever Purge."

42:59.004 --> 43:00.165
Where the hell are we gonna go?

43:00.301 --> 43:02.302
We'll find somewhere safe.

43:02.438 --> 43:03.636
First we help Juan
find his wife,

43:03.771 --> 43:05.876
-then we find somewhere safe.
-

43:06.012 --> 43:07.140
NEWSMAN:
Stay inside your homes.

43:15.753 --> 43:16.890
Gracias.

43:17.026 --> 43:18.288
NEWSMAN: ...they will take
action to stop it.

43:18.424 --> 43:20.956
-But still, no one knows...
-I know where she is.

43:21.092 --> 43:22.289
...who defined this movement.

43:22.424 --> 43:24.095
-

43:26.196 --> 43:29.430
WOMAN:
Ever After. Ever After.

43:30.499 --> 43:32.866
This is the first...

43:33.002 --> 43:35.539
real... Purge.

43:38.679 --> 43:40.040
It's never gonna stop.

43:42.286 --> 43:45.153
Let me fucking go!

44:07.507 --> 44:09.771
Shit.

44:09.907 --> 44:11.747
It's blocked.

44:15.647 --> 44:17.245
Hold on.

44:17.380 --> 44:19.386
The station is
just a few blocks away.

44:19.522 --> 44:21.823
I hope she'll be there.

44:22.855 --> 44:25.222
We can walk from here.

44:34.262 --> 44:35.296
You go get your wife.

44:35.432 --> 44:36.562
We'll stay here
and protect the truck.

44:36.698 --> 44:39.034
But you move fast.
It's not safe here.

44:39.170 --> 44:40.472
You don't need to wait for us.

44:40.607 --> 44:41.777
Yes, we do.

44:43.744 --> 44:45.407
I'm coming with you.

44:46.715 --> 44:48.307
You don't have to do that.

44:48.443 --> 44:51.714
No, you don't have to do that.

44:51.849 --> 44:53.855
Yeah, I do.

44:55.019 --> 44:56.726
They saved our lives.

44:58.892 --> 45:00.721
We'll be right here. Now go.

45:00.857 --> 45:02.699
Come on.

45:14.403 --> 45:16.244
T.T.:
I'll take the back.

45:16.380 --> 45:18.180
Come on, guys.

45:18.315 --> 45:20.145
This side.

45:25.281 --> 45:26.617
Verga.

45:31.124 --> 45:33.086
-

45:35.762 --> 45:38.966
That is a .30-06.

45:42.635 --> 45:44.536
.30-30.

45:44.671 --> 45:46.308
Yeah, yeah.

45:48.245 --> 45:49.708
AR-15.

45:49.843 --> 45:52.214
Listen to that rhythm.

45:52.349 --> 45:54.349
That is a Glock.

45:58.449 --> 46:00.521
-Listen to that bass.
-

46:00.656 --> 46:02.323
Double-barrel shotgun.

46:03.755 --> 46:05.795
AK-47.

46:10.595 --> 46:13.994
Homegrown music from
the heartland right there.

46:17.138 --> 46:19.869
That is American music,
motherfucker.

46:23.043 --> 46:24.810
-MAN: Damn!

46:24.946 --> 46:26.678
-Oh!

46:26.814 --> 46:29.648
Strike up the band!

46:29.784 --> 46:32.512
The symphony sings!

46:32.648 --> 46:34.056
DEPUTY:
Hold on! We're under attack!

46:35.551 --> 46:37.057
-Dispatch!

46:37.192 --> 46:38.822
We're outside the precinct!
Request backup!

46:38.957 --> 46:40.225
Boom, boom, boom!

46:54.745 --> 46:56.505
-

47:13.693 --> 47:14.724
What?

47:14.859 --> 47:16.758
Okay.

47:16.894 --> 47:18.598
Honey...

47:18.734 --> 47:20.593
I need you to take this.

47:20.729 --> 47:22.434
Don't ask any questions,
not right now.

47:22.570 --> 47:24.101
I'm gonna get out the car.
I need you to lock the door.

47:24.236 --> 47:26.099
-Okay.
-I'll be right back.

48:23.500 --> 48:24.593
Open up, bitch.

49:03.806 --> 49:05.708
-Baby!
-

49:05.843 --> 49:07.603
-No!
-

49:26.522 --> 49:28.729
-Yeah!
-Cover me!

49:28.865 --> 49:32.067
Go, go, go! Forever Purge!

49:36.404 --> 49:38.000
-You're fucking dead, puta!

49:45.010 --> 49:46.180
Get off me!

49:49.081 --> 49:50.079
You're a pig!

49:50.215 --> 49:52.681
Get the fuck off of me!

49:53.987 --> 49:55.751
Stop fighting it!

49:56.588 --> 49:59.120
-Get the fuck off of me!
-

50:11.939 --> 50:12.807
Motherfucker!

50:14.940 --> 50:16.577
Help me!

50:16.712 --> 50:18.674
Fucking pig!

50:20.408 --> 50:21.875
Kill him!

50:41.697 --> 50:42.834
-Move.
-MAN: Forever Purge!

50:42.969 --> 50:44.436
Open it up!

50:44.571 --> 50:46.399
-Get out of the way!
-WOMAN: Ever After!

50:52.941 --> 50:54.809
-DARIUS: What was that?

50:57.785 --> 50:58.785
Juan?

50:58.920 --> 51:00.412
-Adela.
-Juan!

51:00.547 --> 51:02.821
Juan! Juan.

51:08.426 --> 51:10.726
MAN:
Purge forever!

51:15.666 --> 51:17.165
-ADELA: De nada.
-!Vamos!

51:17.300 --> 51:19.075
Over here!

51:26.674 --> 51:28.308
The truck is coming!

51:28.443 --> 51:29.514
It's Dylan!

51:29.649 --> 51:31.615
Truck! Get in the truck!

51:32.418 --> 51:34.517
-Get in!
-The truck! Come in!

51:34.653 --> 51:36.792
-Come on, boss.
-No! Find safety now!

51:36.927 --> 51:38.360
I need to get to my family.

51:38.495 --> 51:40.229
-We'll help you.

51:40.364 --> 51:42.624
I'll move faster on my own.
I'll be fine. Just go.

51:42.760 --> 51:43.924
-JUAN: Go, go, go, go!
-Come on!

51:46.097 --> 51:46.965
Here.

51:47.100 --> 51:48.133
You saved my life.

51:48.269 --> 51:49.165
-Thank you, Darius.
-Okay.

51:49.301 --> 51:50.463
JUAN:
Adela!

51:53.003 --> 51:55.307
-

52:55.029 --> 52:57.239
Okay, let's grab
everything we can.

53:00.868 --> 53:02.772
T.T.:
Peanut butter?

53:07.951 --> 53:09.581
You found the jelly.

53:10.853 --> 53:12.518
This could work.

53:36.942 --> 53:38.439
NEWSWOMAN
As the violence escalates

53:38.575 --> 53:39.776
across the country,

53:39.911 --> 53:42.149
we are still trying
to get more information.

53:42.285 --> 53:43.349
NEWSMAN:
That's right, Ruth.

53:43.485 --> 53:44.849
And we are still trying
to figure out

53:44.985 --> 53:48.519
if this Forever Purge was
coordinated or spontaneous.

53:48.655 --> 53:50.484
Various hashtags--
#TooMuchHate,

53:50.619 --> 53:52.355
#OneDayNotEnough--

53:52.491 --> 53:53.857
are all over the Internet.

53:53.992 --> 53:56.793
Fringe conspiracy groups
supporting the Forever Purge

53:56.928 --> 53:59.799
are calling for
a new America to emerge from...

53:59.934 --> 54:01.567
Adela.

54:02.901 --> 54:05.604
I'm scared to have my baby
in this world.

54:05.740 --> 54:08.105
NEWSMAN: Freedom to hate.
Freedom to purge.

54:08.240 --> 54:09.639
Freedom to die.

54:09.775 --> 54:12.273
The NFFA has advised
that anyone

54:12.409 --> 54:15.146
displaying the Ever After flag
will be arrested immediately.

54:15.282 --> 54:17.878
We're in this together.

54:18.014 --> 54:19.617
-Breaking news.

54:19.752 --> 54:21.818
We've just gotten word
that the NFFA

54:21.953 --> 54:23.986
has declared martial law
across the country.

54:24.121 --> 54:26.822
U.S. military will be sent
into nearly every city

54:26.958 --> 54:29.021
to stop the violence
and restore peace.

54:29.157 --> 54:30.558
Citizens are being told
to relinq...

54:30.694 --> 54:31.927
JUAN:
¿Bueno?

54:33.936 --> 54:34.901
!Bueno!

54:43.537 --> 54:47.180
Wait. Juan, I can't understand
what you're saying.

54:47.316 --> 54:49.215
Come on. The-the cell things.

54:51.122 --> 54:53.179
-Towers?
-Yeah, the towers.

54:53.314 --> 54:55.051
The-the cell towers.
They are cutting them.

54:55.187 --> 54:58.551
Hey. We just watched that
a lot of cities have gone dark.

54:58.687 --> 55:00.357
Miami's gone.

55:00.492 --> 55:02.163
Austin is under siege.

55:02.298 --> 55:03.328
First responders
are overwhelmed.

55:03.464 --> 55:04.328
We're in a state of emergency.

55:04.464 --> 55:05.895
It's all over the country.

